Parameters: A status code indicating the result of the operation.
The ID of the message which was sent.

onRealTimeMessageSent(int, int, java.lan.Description: Called to notify the client that a reliable message was sent for a room. Possible status codes include: @B_com#google#android#gms#games#GamesStatusCodes#STATUS_OK_E@ if the message was successfully sent. @B_com#google#android#gms#games#GamesStatusCodes#STATUS_REAL_TIME_MESSAGE_SEND_FAILED_E@ if the attempt to send message failed due to network error. @B_com#google#android#gms#games#GamesStatusCodes#STATUS_REAL_TIME_ROOM_NOT_JOINED_E@ if the attempt to send message failed because the user has not joined the room.

ClassDesc: The listener for callback that is called when a reliable message is sent successfully.
